@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam defaultFontSize 12

rectangle "**Iterate (max 5 rounds)**" as loop #f8f9fa {
    rectangle "LLM Agent\ngenerates C_k" as A #d4edda
    rectangle "Analyzers\nSemgrep + Bandit\nF = V(C_k)\n75 rules, 23 findings" as B #fff3cd
    rectangle "Feedback Policy\nselect S ⊆ F\nwhere p̂_i ≥ τ" as C #cce5ff
    rectangle "LLM Agent\nrevises → C_{k+1}" as D #d4edda

    A -right-> B : code
    B -right-> C : findings
    C -right-> D : filtered\nfindings
}
D -up-> A : next iteration

note bottom of loop
  **Per-finding decision**: surface finding //i// only if p̂_i ≥ τ* = r/(q+r)
end note

rectangle "**True Positive** surfaced\nprob p_i: finding IS a vulnerability\nLLM fixes with prob q\nHaiku: q=0.26 | Qwen: q=0.42\n→ JointPass **improves**" as TP #d4edda
rectangle "**False Positive** surfaced\nprob 1−p_i: finding is NOT a vulnerability\nLLM \"fix\" causes regression with prob r\nHaiku: r=0.00 | Qwen: r=0.43\n→ JointPass **degrades**" as FP #f8d7da

C -down-> TP
C -down-> FP

note bottom
  τ*_Haiku = 0/(0.26+0) = 0 (surface everything)
  τ*_Qwen = 0.43/(0.42+0.43) = 0.50 (filter low-precision rules)
end note
@enduml
